armake

Usage:
    armake binarize [-f] [-i <includefolder>] <source> <target>
    armake build [-f] [-p] [-i <includefolder>] <source> <target>
    armake (-h | --help)
    armake (-v | --version)

Commands:
    binarize     Binarize a file
    build        Pack a folder into a PBO

Options:
    -f --force      Overwrite the target file/folder if it already exists
    -p --packonly   Don't binarize models, configs etc.
    -i --include    Folder to search for includes, defaults to CWD
    -h --help       Show usage information and exit
    -v --version    Print the version number and exit
